| SAP Field          | FinSight Field    | Data Type | Required | Transformation | Validation         |
| ------------------ | ----------------- | --------- | -------- | -------------- | ------------------ |
| Customer Number    | customerId        | String    | Yes      | Direct         | Mandatory          |
| Customer Name      | customerName      | String    | Yes      | Trim           | Mandatory          |
| Company Code       | companyCode       | String    | Yes      | Direct         | Company Exists     |
| Invoice Number     | invoiceId         | String    | Yes      | Direct         | Unique             |
| Invoice Date       | invoiceDate       | Date      | Yes      | YYYY-MM-DD     | Valid Date         |
| Due Date           | dueDate           | Date      | Yes      | YYYY-MM-DD     | Due ≥ Invoice Date |
| Currency           | currency          | String    | Yes      | ISO 4217       | Currency           |
| Invoice Amount     | invoiceAmount     | Decimal   | Yes      | Round(2)       | Positive           |
| Received Amount    | receivedAmount    | Decimal   | No       | Round(2)       | ≥ 0                |
| Outstanding Amount | outstandingAmount | Decimal   | Yes      | Calculated     | Invoice − Received |
